args: ＂In love, you're unstoppable—and the one\nyou fancy will sit up and take notice.\nGo get 'im, snuggle bunny!＂
What is it, Your Highness? Are you hurt?!
LUCA! Bring a healer at once!
What could have happened to him?!
What have you done, you foul, fluffy\ndemon?! What have you done to\nHis Highness?!
Nope! I feel perfectly normal—and more\nspecifically, I feel like the guy who loves\nTHIS gal more than anything!
This isn't any mere anger, but the wrath\nof a woman scorned!
Who cares what the hell ya call it?!\nHelp me stop her before we all end up\nas a steamin' pile'a charcoal briquettes!
My apologies, Your Highness.\nThe fault here is mine alone.
What could you ever have to apologize for,\nsugar lips? I'm just glad you're not hurt.
It's my life's work to keep you safe, babe.
Aw, is my babe blushing? That's adorable!
Apologies, but I must excuse myself!
Heh heh. Ain't she just the cutest?
(My pulse races to hear those words...\nTo have His Highness treat me so.)
(Thanks to that damnable omikuji,\nI've made naught but trouble for everyone.\nAnd yet...I am enjoying it?)
Your Highness?! What is the matter?
The battlefield is a dangerous place,\nand I'm not letting you risk your\nbeautiful neck out there.
But I am a Paladyn! I swore an oath to\nprotect people from harm, and am one\nof our strongest warriors besides!
Nope! Noooot happening. You'll need to\nfind some other chickee to be your cannon\nfodder today, Luca.
I can't believe this is... Fine, whatever.\nYo, everybody! I need help over here!
Are you well satisfied now that you have\nstolen away my darling's heart with your\nfoul and wretched sorcery?!
Was your love for him always this cheap?\nThis selfish?! You...you...you FLOOZY!
(The prince treats me differently than all\nthe others now—almost as if I were some\nhelpless storybook princess.)
(Is this truly what I was striving for all\nthis time? Is it what I truly WANT?)
Don't you dare ignore me, Elisanne!\nWhat are you going to do about this?!
